Our 'Check‚Äìin and Chat' call operatives are on hand to provide practical and emotional support. We endeavour to ensure that people are getting the help they need during lockdown periods and beyond.

Taken into hospital I heard about preparations for lockdown. Stories of run on toilet rolls and shop shortages.  This didn‚Äôt seem like the world I‚Äôd just left. 

The world seemed weird.

With CSF leaking I prepared for surgery. 

Cancelled once. I waited. 

Over the weekend I waited. 

I could leave the hospital provided I wore a mask. Passers by looked at me as some strange person. 

Monday the country went into lockdown. Surgery cancelled. I went home.
